-- Lafarge Cement of Nigeria First-Half Profit Rises 18% Even as Sales Drop
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-30T10:17:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/lafarge-cement-of-nigeria-first-half-profit-rises-18-even-as-sales-drop.html

          
          
             Lafarge Cement Plc of Nigeria said
first-half profit rose to 4.02 billilon naira from 3.42 billion
naira a year earlier, according to a statement e-mailed by the
Lagos-based Nigerian Stock Exchange today.  
 Sales declined to 23 billion naira from 25 billion naira a
year earlier, according to the statement.  
          
          


  


        